{
  "an1.188-197:1.0.1": "\"Etadaggaṁ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṁ bhikkhūnaṁ rattaññūnaṁ yadidaṁ aññāsikoṇḍañño.(1)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.2": "…   Mahāpaññānaṁ yadidaṁ sāriputto.(2)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.3": "…   Iddhimantānaṁ yadidaṁ mahāmoggallāno.(3)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.4": "…   Dhutavādānaṁ yadidaṁ mahākassapo.(4)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.5": "…   Dibbacakkhukānaṁ yadidaṁ anuruddho.(5)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.6": "…   Uccākulikānaṁ yadidaṁ bhaddiyo kāḷigodhāya putto.(6)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.7": "…   Mañjussarānaṁ yadidaṁ lakuṇḍaka bhaddiyo.(7)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.8": "…   Sīhanādikānaṁ yadidaṁ piṇḍolabhāradvājo.(8)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.9": "…   Dhammakathikānaṁ yadidaṁ puṇṇo mantāṇiputto.(9)",
  "an1.188-197:1.0.10": "…   Saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṁ vibhajantānaṁ yadidaṁ mahākaccāno\"ti.(10)"
}